flowchart TD
    input["用户输入\n（string | ContentBlock[]）"]
    ultraplan{feature ULTRAPLAN\n且含关键词?}
    bash_mode{mode === bash\n或 ! 前缀?}
    slash{startsWith / ?}
    text["processTextPrompt()\n→ UserMessage\n→ 触发 LLM 调用"]
    bash_exec["processBashCommand()\n→ 本地执行\n→ SystemLocalCommandMessage"]
    slash_exec["processSlashCommand()\n→ 命令执行\n→ SystemLocalCommandMessage"]
    ultraplan_exec["路由到 /ultraplan\n→ 远程 Plan 会话"]

    input --> ultraplan
    ultraplan -->|是| ultraplan_exec
    ultraplan -->|否| bash_mode
    bash_mode -->|是| bash_exec
    bash_mode -->|否| slash
    slash -->|是| slash_exec
    slash -->|否| text
